name: Catson
description: $CAT, the most fun and interesting cat on the BASE blockchain. Catson is a character on the Base blockchain, known for his fun-loving and carefree personality. He is part of the Boys Club gang, along with Pepe and Brett, who are supporting the rise of the $CAT token. The project emphasizes community ownership and decentralization. The $CAT token launched on a fairlaunch launchpad and has a total supply of 1,000,000,000, with liquidity burned and the contract renounced. 57% of the total supply has been bought and burned, first of it's kind.
